general.description:
u&u: our name says it all. We take the time to connect what really matters for both our clients (u) and our candidates (&u), with long-term relationships in mind. Our purpose is to change lives by connecting potential with opportunity – for our clients, our candidates, and our team. With offices in Queensland and across New South Wales, u&u was recognised by SEEK as the National Medium Sized Recruitment Agency of the Year, was independently voted as the Executive Recruiter of the Year by HRD Magazine in 2017, and has been named by the Financial Review as one of the top 50 fastest growing businesses in 2015, 2016 and 2017.

At u&u, we specialise in permanent, contracting and project recruitment across the following sectors:
•	Accounting & Finance;
•	Business Support (Administration);
•	Construction & Property;
•	Digital;
•	Engineering;
•	Health, Safety & Environment;
•	Human Resources;
•	Information Technology;
•	Legal, Risk & Compliance;
•	Marketing & Communications;
•	Procurement, Contracts & Supply;
•	Sales; and
•	Senior Executive.

Want to learn more about u&u? Check us out at www.uandu.com

